{"tid":2332148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"朝幹部嘲金正恩「二兒媳」","createTime":"2020-12-19T11:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T11:30:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2a39a59a66645e8552f0581d597202d0086815","tid":2332148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:22:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201219/CK7TD4TT75FQTH2MLB5WNX25SA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FCK7TD4TT75FQTH2MLB5WNX25SA%2F&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWCBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=b4bd22b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201219%2FCK7TD4TT75FQTH2MLB5WNX25SA%2F&h=c45e3e49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201219/CK7TD4TT75FQTH2MLB5WNX25SA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n朝幹部嘲金正恩「二兒媳」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MVz1hhlGjMW4sGIdgYDKeXH8ANA=/640x395/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XKXJI2MLTFF3NI4NPZUQE5EDZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMVz1hhlGjMW4sGIdgYDKeXH8ANA%3D%2F640x395%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXKXJI2MLTFF3NI4NPZUQE5EDZQ.jpg&h=21be5cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■金正恩<br />\n<br />\n南韓統一部的北韓信息門戶網站「朝鮮通」，最近整理整體菜單以便瀏覽查閱，其中在「北韓暗語」欄目，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人不如故」暗喻不滿<br />\n<br />\n據「北韓暗語」欄目指，北韓幹部之間談及金正恩，常避忌不直呼其名，而是用這暗語，像「二兒媳的命令」和「二兒媳的指示」等。自由亞洲電台之前曾引用北韓內部消息，指這暗語是源於俗語「娶了二兒媳才懂得大媳婦的情誼」，意思類似「衣不如新，人不如故」，把上任領袖金正日比作「大媳婦」，金正恩稱為「二兒媳」，是展示他們對金正恩不滿；該報道又指北韓一些地方流行的暗語「平壤鏡子」，指的是「人的腳掌，意思是。。。。。。。。。」，以此貶低把首都平壤建設視為最大政績的金正恩。<br />\n<br />\n據南韓《朝鮮日報》報道，「朝鮮通」網站將北韓暗語分了多個類別，如「全體黨幹部和特權階層的相關暗語」、「北韓當局政策和居民控制的相關暗語」、「性相關暗語」等，但暫時只發佈「二兒媳」一個暗語。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《朝鮮日報》"},{"pid":"50926a35e76012e6a1509620e5fc86089e8beb61","tid":2332148,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">朝幹部準備花式自殺</span>"},{"pid":"3351fc60ceb0426e721c49df9b1c00f5e9f095d9","tid":2332148,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"又係金將軍展示創意嘅時候"}]}